text: The Dallas Athletic Conference is a conference within the National Junior College Athletic Association Region 5. The conference consists of six junior colleges located in Dallas County, Texas. ==Members== Member institutions are Brookhaven College, Cedar Valley College, Eastfield College, Mountain View College, North Lake College, and Richland College. Sports for men are baseball, basketball, golf, soccer, and tennis. Sports for women are soccer, tennis, and volleyball. ==External links== * Dallas Athletic Conference Home ==See also== *National Junior College Athletic Association ==References== Category:NJCAA conferences Category:College sports in Texas Category:Sports in Dallas
